OL,6,FA compulsive gambler is calling for
OL,7,Fgreater regulation of the Channel
OL,8,FIslands Lottery and the sale of
OL,9,FChristmas lottery tickets.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Channel anonymously,
OL,12,Fhe said: "It's the fact that you are
OL,13,Falmost pressured into buying a scratch
OL,14,Fcards and lottery tickets... It
OL,15,Fdoesn't matter where you go and they
OL,16,Fare sitting by the tills like an
OL,17,Fimpulse buy.
