OL,3,CCalls to change Channel Islands
OL,4,CLottery laws
OL,6,F"For someone who is a compulsive
OL,7,Fgambler that gets quite difficult...
OL,8,Fevery time you go into the shops you
OL,9,Fare being asked".
OL,11,FThe interviewee started gambling when
OL,12,Fthey were 8 years old at Jersey's
OL,13,Fpenny arcades. Now, in his 50s, they
OL,14,Fstill struggle around Christmas.
OL,16,FIn the UK, there are some tighter
OL,17,Fregulations around the sale and
OL,18,Fadvertisement of scratch cards.
