OL,3,CCalls to change Channel Islands
OL,4,CLottery laws
OL,6,F#10 scratch cards were banned in the
OL,7,FUK and there are limits on the number
OL,8,Fthat you can buy.
OL,10,FChannel Island sellers get a
OL,11,Fcommission from the tickets, but the
OL,12,Foperator says it does not encourage
OL,13,Fthem to ask customers if they want to
OL,14,Fplay.
OL,16,FLast year, around two and a half
OL,17,Fmillion pounds was raised for good
OL,18,Fcauses by the Channel Islands lottery
OL,19,Fincluding the Christmas draw.
