OL,3,CCalls to change Channel Islands
OL,4,CLottery laws
OL,6,FDeputy Charles Parkinson, Chair of the
OL,7,FChannel Islands Lottery sub-committee,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are going to be rolling out
OL,9,Fin the next two or three weeks a
OL,10,Ftraining programme for resellers to
OL,11,Fhelp them identify any customers who
OL,12,Fhave a problem with buying lottery
OL,13,Ftickets".
OL,15,FEarlier this year, a research was
OL,16,Fcommissioned to determine the impact
OL,17,Fgambling has across the Channel
OL,18,FIslands - with residents asked what
OL,19,Fthey would like to see changed.
