OL,4,CLottery laws
OL,6,FIt comes as the main contracts for the
OL,7,Flottery are up for renew in 2027.
OL,9,FDeputy Charles Parkinson, who chairs
OL,10,Fthe States Trading Supervisory Board
OL,11,Fwhich is responsible for overseeing
OL,12,Fthe lottery in Guernsey said this will
OL,13,Fprovide an opportunity to reshape the
OL,14,Fgames if they feel the need to do so.
