OL,3,CCalls to change Channel Islands
OL,4,CLottery laws
OL,6,FHead of the Channel Islands Lottery,
OL,7,FJon Taylor said: "Once we gather all
OL,8,Fthe evidence and information that we
OL,9,Fhave - both from a health impact
OL,10,Fscenario and from an opportunity to
OL,11,Fmaximise returns to good causes - all
OL,12,Fthat information will be gathered and
OL,13,Fthat will help inform our decision
OL,14,Fmaking process for the future of the
OL,15,Flottery".
OL,17,FIf you need support, there are local
OL,18,Forganisations who can help.
